1477973 aafter clause (ab), the following clause shall be inserted, namely:- ' (aba)" Budapest Treaty" means the Budapest Treaty on the International Recognition of the Deposit of Micro- organisms for the Purposes of Patent Procedure done at Budapest on 28th day of April, 1977, as amended and modified from time to time;';
